                {
                    "id": "upstream_qualitative_high_corner",
                    "description": "High corner of the upstream `COOxidation: Qualitative - Positive Production and Loss` 3Г—3Г—3 sweep (test_co_oxidation.jl:337-366): OH=1e13, HOв‚‚=1e15, NO=1e18, NOв‚‚=2e18 mвЃ»Ві (CO=2.5e18, Oв‚ѓ=1e18 at defaults). The upstream test asserts L_OH, L_HO2, L_HOx and HO2_ss are all strictly positive вЂ” pinned here at rel=1e-10 (L_OH=2.067e14, L_HO2=8.108e15, L_HOx=2.058e14, HO2_ss=7.407e11, all > 0). Together with `upstream_qualitative_low_corner` this brackets the two extreme corners of the upstream sweep grid; P_O3=8.097e15 and chain_length=39.36 are pinned as extension coverage.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {"OH": 1.0e13, "HO2": 1.0e15, "NO": 1.0e18, "NO2": 2.0e18},
                    "time_span": {"start": 0.0, "end": 1.0},
                    "assertions": [
