                        {"variable": "L_HOx", "time": 0.0, "expected": 558000000000.0},
                        {"variable": "HO2_ss", "time": 0.0, "expected": 59259259259259.266},
                        {"variable": "P_O3", "time": 0.0, "expected": 1679000000000.0},
                        {"variable": "chain_length", "time": 0.0, "expected": 3.629032258064516}
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "no_doubled_scales_no_channels",
                    "description": "NO doubled to 5.0e15 mвЃ»Ві (2Г— default). The HOв‚‚+NO term of L_HO2 doubles its contribution; the gross-production term of P_O3 and the numerator of chain_length are linear in NO. HO2_ss = k_CO_OHВ·COВ·OH/(k_HO2_NOВ·NO) is inversely proportional to NO and halves to 1.481e13. L_OH and L_HOx have no NO dependence and are unchanged. chain_length doubles (numerator в€ќ NO, denominator NO-independent). Verifies the NO-linearity of the propagation channels and the inverse-NO dependence of HO2_ss.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {"NO": 5.0e15},
                    "time_span": {"start": 0.0, "end": 1.0},
                    "assertions": [
                        {"variable": "L_OH", "time": 0.0, "expected": 923000000000.0001},
                        {"variable": "L_HO2", "time": 0.0, "expected": 4308000000000.0},
                        {"variable": "L_HOx", "time": 0.0, "expected": 308000000000.0},
                        {"variable": "HO2_ss", "time": 0.0, "expected": 14814814814814.816},
                        {"variable": "P_O3", "time": 0.0, "expected": 3777000000000.0},
                        {"variable": "chain_length", "time": 0.0, "expected": 13.14935064935065}
                    ]
                },
                {
